<SYNC Start=1380316><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1381276><P Class=ENUSCC>Take care of the lonely lady.
<SYNC Start=1384487><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1385947><P Class=ENUSCC>Here.
<SYNC Start=1386781><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1407427><P Class=ENUSCC>Count Fujiwara asks Miss Hideko<br>to kindly allow her maid Tamako
<SYNC Start=1410346><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
