<SYNC Start=1425862><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1465777><P Class=ENUSCC>You tried to fool me with a fake coin.
<SYNC Start=1467862><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1467946><P Class=ENUSCC>How dare you?
<SYNC Start=1469447><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1474661><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">You think I'm Tamako,<br>a poor Korean handmaiden.</i></font>
