<SYNC Start=1483086><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">Raised by Miss Boksun,<br>top purveyor of stolen goods.</i></font>
<SYNC Start=1489217><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1489300><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">I was able to tell a real coin<br>from a fake when I was 5.</i></font>
