<SYNC Start=1496808><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">and pickpocketing from Kutan,</i></font>
<SYNC Start=1500395><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1501229><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">but these babies will never<br>learn such useful skills.</i></font>
<SYNC Start=1504524><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1505316><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">Abandoned as newborns,</i></font>
<SYNC Start=1507610><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1507694><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">we'll wash and feed them,<br>then sell them to Japan.</i></font>
<SYNC Start=1510822><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1511281><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">What meaningful work.</i></font>
<SYNC Start=1513116><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1513199><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">Instead of starving, they grow up<br>to be rich gentlemen and ladies.</i></font>
<SYNC Start=1517537><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
