<SYNC Start=1523293><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1523751><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">I wish my breasts gave milk.<br>I'd breastfeed all of them.</i></font>
<SYNC Start=1528715><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1538182><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">Count!</i></font>
<SYNC Start=1539267><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1569714><P Class=ENUSCC>I'll tell you the story of an interpreter,
<SYNC Start=1572759><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
