<SYNC Start=1594822><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1595365><P Class=ENUSCC>and adopts his wife's family name Kouzuki.
<SYNC Start=1598701><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1599953><P Class=ENUSCC>Ba... bas...
<SYNC Start=1604207><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1604290><P Class=ENUSCC>That bastard builds a mansion,<br>fills it with books and antiques.
<SYNC Start=1609295><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1611255><P Class=ENUSCC>He invites Japanese collectors<br>to his library,
