<SYNC Start=1838858><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1838941><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">Don't ask! If you ask a question,<br>she'll start to think.</i></font>
<SYNC Start=1842653><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
