<SYNC Start=1993304><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1994847><P Class=ENUSCC>Here, a gift.
<SYNC Start=1995806><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2008069><P Class=ENUSCC>Oh, he's so thoughtful!
<SYNC Start=2010529><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
