<SYNC Start=3184911><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3188873><P Class=ENUSCC>Keep doing what the Count will.
<SYNC Start=3191167><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3194379><P Class=ENUSCC>And this is what he'll say.
<SYNC Start=3197423><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=3200009><P Class=ENUSCC>"It's so soft, warm,
