<SYNC Start=4194253><P Class=ENUSCC>You know what to say.
<SYNC Start=4195462><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4210519><P Class=ENUSCC>Who is that person?
<SYNC Start=4211895><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4212771><P Class=ENUSCC>The Countess Lady Fujiwara.
<SYNC Start=4214439><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4214523><P Class=ENUSCC>Her maiden name was Izumi Hideko.
<SYNC Start=4217276><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4219069><P Class=ENUSCC>And who might you be?
<SYNC Start=4220946><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
