<SYNC Start=4288180><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4323799><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">Good day, Countess.</i></font>
<SYNC Start=4325884><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4326635><P Class=ENUSCC><i><font color="#80ffff">Do you remember me?</i></font>
<SYNC Start=4328220><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4331765><P Class=ENUSCC>Countess?
<SYNC Start=4332599><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4342275><P Class=ENUSCC>What is this?
